statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data;

SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY time_visited DESC;

SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE id = 1 ORDER BY time_visited DESC

SELECT DISTINCT source_url FROM website_traffic_data

SELECT MAX(time_visited) AS latest_visit_time FROM website_traffic_data;

SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE ad_campaign_id IS NOT NULL ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visit_timestamp, ad_campaign_id FROM website_traffic_data WHERE id > 100 ORDER BY visit_timestamp ASC;
SELECT campaign_name, budget FROM ad_campaigns WHERE budget > 5000 ORDER BY campaign_start_date DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, browser_info FROM visitor_details WHERE country_code = 'US' ORDER BY visitor_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT vd.*, wt.page_url FROM visitor_details AS vd JOIN website_traffic_data AS wt ON vd.visitor_id = wt.id AND wt.ad_campaign_id IS NOT NULL ORDER BY wt.visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
SELECT visitor_id, visit_time FROM website_visits ORDER BY visit_time DESC;
SELECT visitor_name, location FROM visitors WHERE device_type = 'Mobile';
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM campaigns WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_url, conversion_rate FROM landing_pages ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits ORDER BY visit_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT visitor_id, count(*) as visit_count FROM website_visits GROUP BY visitor_id ORDER BY visit_count DESC;

SELECT v.visitor_id, v.visitor_name, l.page_url FROM visitors v JOIN website_visits w ON v.visitor_id = w.visitor_id JOIN landing_pages l ON w.landing_page_id = l.landing_page_id WHERE w.visit_time >= '2022-01-01' AND w.visit_time <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT c.campaign_name, count(w.visit_id) as visit_count FROM campaigns c LEFT JOIN website_visits w ON c.campaign_id = w.campaign_id GROUP BY c.campaign_name ORDER BY visit_count DESC;

SELECT v.visitor_name, v.location, l.page_url, c.campaign_name FROM visitors v JOIN website_visits w ON v.visitor_id = w.visitor_id JOIN landing_pages l ON w.landing_page_id = l.landing_page_id JOIN campaigns c ON w.campaign_id = c.campaign_id WHERE c.start_date <= CURRENT_DATE AND c.end_date >= CURRENT_DATE ORDER BY w.visit_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_visits LIMIT 5;
SELECT visit_id, visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_visits WHERE visit_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT channel_name, channel_type, channel_cost FROM marketing_channels ORDER BY channel_cost DESC;
